NodeJS Primer
	. Build scalable network applications using JS on the server side. 
	. Nodejs is built as a wrapper around the V8 runtime engine. 
	. Superfast because its built in C

What can you build: 
	. Websocket server {like a chat server - lots of connections a.k.a chat terminals and sockets stay open }	
	. Fast File upload client. 
	. Ad Server 
	. Any real time data apps

WHat it isnt:
	. Not a web framework
	. for beginners
	. not multi-threaded. 

NodejS is non-blocking code. 
	. The correct functions are kickstarted using CALLback functions
			
